room_title: Escape room "La Famiglia" by The Sanctuary Escape Games in Oklahoma City
room_address: 7650 W Reno Ave Oklahoma City, OK 73128
room_description:
Since your induction into the family you’ve climbed the ranks quickly and have settled into your newly promoted role as Consigliere or Chief Advisor. This is the highest position you can attain without being directly related to the Pantano family.
Today is a sad day as you are attending Uncle Julio Fiorentino’s funeral. After the ceremony, you are instructed to get back to Giovanni’s deli asap to pick up the food for the reception.
